Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(640,639)}Bonjour
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,克克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我居然睡过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,圣翔祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,终于快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,克克听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下次圣翔祭 BANANA要参与后场布置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你们用那些买通BANANA啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,贿赂真是没品味呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我就给绿色的马卡龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 克克去年当过主角了 不准再当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,行行 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,华恋先回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 小光听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小光 为什么要把我关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我做错了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会是生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小光 虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,天黑了 吃饭时间也到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先消消气谈谈吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我这样吃不了啊
