Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在的表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
